  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Kashmir Potato Agri-Business Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Farmers</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project Goal: Organize potato farmers into business oriented groups, increase their business capacity and agricultural productivity, and use lessons learned to strengthen the potato sector
Activities: (1) Provide technical support including procurement and distribution of higher quality potato seeds and fertilizers amongst targeted farmers, (2) provide training in better management of farming techniques, creating of two demonstration plots in each targeted cluster, (4) provide instruction on disease and pest management, and (5) conduct business and marketing skills training.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Potato Agribusiness Project aims to help 600 marginalized farmers through building business capacity and agricultural productivity.</narrative>
  </description>
